                                </h3>
                                <p className="desktop-only" style={{
                                    color: '#666',
                                    marginBottom: '20px',
                                    lineHeight: '1.5'
                                }}>
                                    ‚Ä¢ √âcoutez la phrase cr√©√©e<br/>
